tv.matchstick.flint
类 MediaInfo

java.lang.Object
  tv.matchstick.flint.MediaInfo

public final class MediaInfo
extends java.lang.Object

Contain all Media informations. Use MediaInfo.Builder to build an instance of this class. MediaInfo is used by RemoteMediaPlayer to load media on the receiver application.
